Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:37.59,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(100,100)}{\blur2}你眼中的那个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:43.92,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur2}どんな色をしてるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:43.92,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(100,100)}{\blur2}有着怎样的色彩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:45.63,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur2}<Measure feeling match>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:45.63,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(100,100)}{\blur2}<Measure feeling match>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:51.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur2}失くす痛みなんて 慣れたくは無いのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:51.50,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(100,100)}{\blur2}明明不愿感受习惯 失去的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:56.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur2}こんな夜も星はきれいだね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:56.10,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(100,100)}{\blur2}这样的夜晚 星空依旧绚烂
